package: Zigbee
description: Silicon Labs implementation of the Scenes client cluster.  The component is only
  intended to assist with debugging, as the implemented callbacks simply parse responses
  from the Scenes server and print the results. Before production, this component
  should be replaced with code that acts on the responses in an appropriate way.
id: zigbee_scenes_client
label: Scenes Client Cluster
category: Zigbee|Cluster Library|Common
quality: production
provides:
   - name: "zigbee_scenes_client"
source:
  - path: protocol/zigbee/app/framework/plugin/scenes-client/scenes-client.c
include:
  - path: protocol/zigbee/app/framework/plugin/scenes-client
    file_list:
      - path: scenes-client.h
template_contribution:
  - name: component_catalog
    value: zigbee_scenes_client
  - name: cluster_service
    value:
       cluster_id: "0x0005"
       mfg_id: "NOT_MFG_SPECIFIC"
       side: "CLIENT"
       service_function: "emberAfScenesClusterClientCommandParse"

documentation:
  docset: zigbee
  document: zigbee-af-api/scenes-client
